      <h1>Quickstart</h1>
      <p>Cloudbox is designed for the seven-minute test: deploy it, open one URL, inspect a complete synthetic computer, then generate another one.</p>
      <pre><code>bun install
bun alchemy dev</code></pre>
      <p>The app starts with a seeded full-paper run, so local development does not depend on an external model key.</p>
